  "time_ut": 1661261418,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0da2\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d89\u0da9 \u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d88\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "By allowing the regime to take revenge, the President is alienating the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr Pathum Karner, a specialist who is involved in the Gallumuwadora struggle, says that by taking revenge on the fighters and allowing the regime to take revenge, the new president is further alienating the people from him. From his Twitter account, he further says that the President has no ability to solve the crisis through that."
      ],
